name: shade
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "shade" %}
{% set version = "1.33.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/shade-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 36f6936da93723f34bf99d00bae24aa4cc36125d597392ead8319720035d21e8

build:
  number: 2
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pbr >=2.0.0
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - openstacksdk >=0.15.0
    - os-client-config >=1.28.0
    - pbr !=2.1.0,>=2.0.0
    # extras
    - munch
    - decorator
    - jmespath
    - jsonpatch
    - keystoneauth1
    - requestsexceptions
    - dogpile.cache
    - simplejson
    - netifaces
    - python-ironicclient

test:
  imports:
    - shade
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://docs.openstack.org/developer/shade/
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Client library for OpenStack containing Infra business logic
  dev_url: https://github.com/openstack-infra/shade.git
  doc_url: https://docs.openstack.org/shade/latest/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - brainstorm
